### Quick Vouch API Tests
### Make sure server is running on localhost:3000

### 1. Get all vouches (public)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/vouches?page=1&limit=5

### 2. Get vouch statistics (public)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/vouches/stats

### 3. Search vouches (public)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/vouches?search=amazing

### 4. Filter by rating (public)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/vouches?rating=5&isVerified=true

### 5. Get single vouch (replace with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/vouches/cmdv6wtwq000aa52b7cakx8in

### 6. Login to get admin token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "vouchadmin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 7. Seed vouches (admin only - use token from step 6)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/vouches/seed
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Create new vouch (admin only - use token from step 6)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/vouches
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "quicktest",
  "avatarSeed": "quicktest",
  "rating": 4,
  "reviewText": "Quick test vouch from API",
  "isVerified": false,
  "status": "PENDING"
} 